From 7ad1d1030480b80a3a88b28e22a37f366caa8e48 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Gerasim Troeglazov <3dEyes@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 20 Oct 2023 12:19:25 +1000
Subject: Haiku build setup


